  "description": "The full parameter exploration preset. Each macro engages a different body character and dimension of the trench. PRESSURE=hydrostatic compression + sub depth. CREATURE=bioluminescent life. WRECK=metal hull / industrial body character. ABYSS=darkness filter sweep. Together they survey the complete trench from surface wreckage to hadal floor.",
