    "revelation": null,
    "god": null,
    "flock_note": "Start all macros at 0.5. Then explore each dimension independently. WRECK macro at 0.5 puts you inside a corroded hull (bodyChar=2 with mix=0.65). PRESSURE at 0.8+ brings the hadal compression. CREATURE at 0.7 lights the bioluminescent field. ABYSS sweeps the filter toward darkness. This is the orientation preset — the full map of the engine.",
    "diagnosis": "Default macro values set at 0.5/0.5/0.5/0.5 for balanced exploration. filterCutoff=320: mid-depth starting point. bodyChar=2 (Wreck) as the default character — the most distinctive sonic identity. bioMix=0.3 at rest: the life is present but not dominant. All parameters calibrated for maximum macro responsiveness. This is the teaching preset."
